data.description: Welcome home! This four sided brick home offers a perfect blend of timeless elegance and modern comfort. Situated on a sprawling acre lot in a tranquil cul-de-sac in Douglasville, this property provides serenity of suburban living with the convenient access to many amenities within a five mile drive. This is your opportunity to embrace peace, comfort and the beauty of nature. Don't miss your chance to make this your dream home!
